{"word":"καλάμη","slug":"καλάμη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n52489\" key=\"kala/mh\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κᾰλᾰ´μ-η</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, (v. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κάλαμος</foreign>) <sense id=\"n52489.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stalk</tr_>, esp. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the stalk</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">straw of corn</tr_>, metaph. in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἶψά τε φυλόπιδος πέλεται κόρος ἀνθρώποισιν, ἧς τε πλείστην μὲν καλάμην Χθονὶ Χαλκὸς ἔχευεν, ἄμητος δ᾽ ὀλίγιστος</foreign>, i.e. when there is much <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">straw</tr_> and little harvest, much <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">slaughter</tr_> and little profit, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:19:222\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.222</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κ. πυρῶν</foreign> wheat-<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">straw</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:33\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.33</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σῖτος σὺν τῇ καλάμῃ ἀποκείμενος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:5:4:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.4.27</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">καλάμαν τε καὶ ἱερὰ δράγματα . . ἀσταχύων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0533.tlg002:20\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Call.\">Call.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cer.\">Cer.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; prov. of a greedy farmer, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πυροὺς ἐπὶ καλάμῃ ἀροῦν</foreign> to exhaust ground by one corn-crop after another, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0540.tlg036:77\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">77</biblScope> </bibl>: pl., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σῖτος ἐπὶ ταῖς κ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0081.tlg001:5:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.H.\">D.H.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.13</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n52489.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stubble</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg026:341b:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mete.\">Mete.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">341b27</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,PSI:4:380:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PSI\">PSI</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.380.6</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B.C.)</date>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0031.tlg007.perseus-grc1:3:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"tit